dct_description_sm: Is likely sheet of the Central Provinces Revenue Survey, though possibly a publication of Great Indian Peninsula Railway Company
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian
Bar scale in furlongs and miles
Shows towns, villages, forts, roads and paths, vegetation, cultivation, waterways, ravines, railway, points of interest such as gardens and mines
